POLIOMYELITIS UPDATE (21): WPV1 ACUTE FLACCID PARALYSIS PAKISTAN, CVDPV2 ACUTE FLACCID PARALYSIS (CHAD, DEMOCRATIC REPUBLIC OF CONGO, NIGER, YEMEN) POSITIVE ENVIRONMENTAL SAMPLES (DJIBOUTI, GHANA, NIGERIA, SOMALIA)
